# Filamentory Project Structure

This workspace has two apps: a TypeScript/Express backend and a React/Vite frontend.

## Backend
- Entry point: [backend/src/server.ts](mdc:backend/src/server.ts)
- HTTP routes:
  - Auth: [backend/src/routes/auth.ts](mdc:backend/src/routes/auth.ts)
  - Filaments: [backend/src/routes/filaments.ts](mdc:backend/src/routes/filaments.ts)
  - Notes: [backend/src/routes/notes.ts](mdc:backend/src/routes/notes.ts)
- Services:
  - Database (SQLite): [backend/src/services/database.ts](mdc:backend/src/services/database.ts)
  - Auth: [backend/src/services/authService.ts](mdc:backend/src/services/authService.ts)
  - Tokens/JWT: [backend/src/services/tokenService.ts](mdc:backend/src/services/tokenService.ts)
  - Email (Resend): [backend/src/services/emailService.ts](mdc:backend/src/services/emailService.ts)
- Middleware:
  - Auth: [backend/src/middleware/auth.ts](mdc:backend/src/middleware/auth.ts)
  - Rate limiting: [backend/src/middleware/rateLimiter.ts](mdc:backend/src/middleware/rateLimiter.ts)
- Config:
  - Swagger/OpenAPI: [backend/src/config/swagger.ts](mdc:backend/src/config/swagger.ts)
  - Email env: [backend/src/config/email.ts](mdc:backend/src/config/email.ts)
  - JWT/cookies: [backend/src/config/jwt.ts](mdc:backend/src/config/jwt.ts)

Notes:
- SQLite DB file lives under `backend/data/filaments.db`.
- JSON data migration is removed; ignore any references to `filaments.json` or `notes.json`.

## Frontend
- Vite app entry: [frontend/src/main.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/main.tsx)
- Root app: [frontend/src/App.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/App.tsx)
- UI components: [frontend/src/components](mdc:frontend/src/components)
- Contexts: [frontend/src/contexts](mdc:frontend/src/contexts)
- API clients: [frontend/src/services](mdc:frontend/src/services)
- Types: [frontend/src/types](mdc:frontend/src/types)

Auth-related frontend:
- Context: [frontend/src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx)
- Login & code entry: [frontend/src/components/auth/LoginForm.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/auth/LoginForm.tsx), [frontend/src/components/auth/CodeEntryForm.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/auth/CodeEntryForm.tsx)
- Verify page: [frontend/src/components/auth/VerifyToken.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/auth/VerifyToken.tsx)
- API: [frontend/src/services/authApi.ts](mdc:frontend/src/services/authApi.ts)

